'''尼克·博爾斯'''（{{lang-en|Nick Boles}}，{{bd|1965年|11月2日}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/35373.stm|title=Nicholas Boles MP|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Democracy Live|accessdate=25 July 2010|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306121708/http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/35373.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]政治人物，他的黨籍是[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]。

==生平==
自2010年開始，他擔任[[格蘭瑟姆和斯坦福_(英國國會選區)|格蘭瑟姆和斯坦福]]選區選出的英國下議院議員。他的父親傑克·博爾斯爵士曾在1975年至1983年擔任英國國民信託的主席<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/2012/sep/13/green-belt-land-policy-exchange|location=London, UK|work=The Guardian|first=Nicholas|last=Watt|title=Free up green-belt land for new housing, says Policy Exchange|date=13 September 2012|accessdate=2016-03-08|archive-date=2012-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121204223652/http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/2012/sep/13/green-belt-land-policy-exchange|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2199998/Planning-minister-Nick-Boles-grew-glorious-countryside--wont-say-green-belt-sacrosanct.html|location=London, UK|work=Daily Mail|title=Remember YOUR roots, Mr Boles? New planning minister grew up in glorious countryside... but won't say green belt is sacrosanct|accessdate=2016-03-08|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071519/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2199998/Planning-minister-Nick-Boles-grew-glorious-countryside--wont-say-green-belt-sacrosanct.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

